# ============================================================
# COMPANY VALIDATION ARCHITECTURE
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: architecture
domain: company
scope: company.validation
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines validation architecture for company handling.

## validation_matrix
- identity validation
- ownership validation
- role validation
- activity validation
- state validation
- boundary validation

## validation_principles
Validation exists to prevent
implicit authority,
implicit scope widening,
invalid operational state,
and invalid economic participation.

## required_behavior
- validation must happen before mutation
- validation must happen before privileged execution
- failed validation must produce bounded denial or review
- validation outcomes must remain inspectable

## outcome_model
- pass
- deny
- review-required
- suspend-path
- close-path

## review_checklist
- validation axes are explicit
- outcome model is explicit
- denial/review split is explicit
